1071
01:45:05,007 --> 01:45:07,569
Ti umukni!

1072
01:45:18,795 --> 01:45:20,680
Imate li vatre?

1073
01:45:25,371 --> 01:45:31,780
Ne, ja imam vatre.

1074
01:45:35,466 --> 01:45:38,482
Ave Marija, puna milosti...

